Package: work.tkgstrator.kioueditor
Name: KiouEditor
Version: 1.1.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: KIOU (Shogi) tweak. Unlocks decoration supplies / characters / skins by editing decoded protobuf replies in memory, forces premium kifu analysis / voice playback / friend menu on, and pins the Beginner Support NNUE evaluator (depth, skill, hash) to user-chosen values via an in-game settings sheet. Currency and paid items are never modified. For authorized testing only.
Maintainer: NEVER KNOWS BEST
Author: tkgstrator
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate
